message.raw:
Lots of name cleanups based on reviews.

As pointed out by Carlos, change the DirIter internal pointer
to a unique_ptr, rename DirIterInternal class to DirIterPrivate class to
be consistent with the rest of the code, and rename the "internal"
private member variable to be consistent with the rest of the
code.
